  - Title: Qur’ân
    Location: XLI 37
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Symbolism=Solar Symbolism
---
And of His signs are the night and the day and the sun and the moon.
Adore not the sun nor the moon; but adore Allâh who created them, if
it is in truth Him whom ye worship.
